             They don’t all want to be immigration lawyers, but this year, hundreds of Harvard Law School students have made immigrant rights their business.
            </p>
           </div>
          </div>
          <!-- .entry-meta -->
         </li>
         <li class="bulletin-issue">
          <a class="full-size-link" href="https://today.law.harvard.edu/bulletin/issue/fall-2016/">
          </a>
          <div class="bulletin-issue-cover">
           <a href="https://today.law.harvard.edu/bulletin/issue/fall-2016/" title="Fall 2016">
            <img alt="Fall 2016" src="https://today.law.harvard.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/HLB_fall_16__cover_image-330x429.jpg"/>
           </a>
          </div>
