     <div class="site-content" id="content">
      <div class="content-area" id="primary">
       <main class="site-main panels" id="main" role="main">
        <div class="panels-collection" data-modular-content-collection="">
         <section class="panel panel-parent panel-type-featured_posts panel-odd" data-modular-content="" data-type="featured_posts">
          <div class="panel-container " style="background-color:;">
           <div class="panel-content">
            <div class="panel-title">
             <h4>
              Featured News
             </h4>
            </div>
            <div class="large-featured-post">
             <div class="featured-post-image">
              <a href="https://today.law.harvard.edu/why-i-changed-my-mind/" title="Why I Changed My Mind">
               <img alt="Why I Changed My Mind 4" src="https://today.law.harvard.edu/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/iStock-800020364-web2-570x340.png"/>
              </a>
             </div>
             <h2 class="entry-title">
              <a href="https://today.law.harvard.edu/why-i-changed-my-mind/">
               Why I Changed My Mind
              </a>
             </h2>
             <div class="entry-content">
              <p>
               An HLS panel “Why I Changed My Mind” brought together four faculty members to share their moments of reckoning, when they had to re-examine some of their most closely held ideas.
              </p>
             </div>
            </div>
            <ul class="featured-posts">
             <li class="featured-post">
              <div class="featured-post-image">
               <a href="https://today.law.harvard.edu/redressing-harm-through-restorative-justice/" title="Redressing Harm through Restorative Justice">
